      SUBROUTINE CIRR18                                                 C18  100
C*********************************************************************  C18  110
C*  ROUTINE TO SET CTHIK CALT CEXT  FOR  CIRRUS CLOUDS 18 19        **  C18  120
C*  INPUTS]                                                         **  C18  130
C*           CHTIK    -  CIRRUS THICKNESS (KM)                      **  C18  140
C*                       0 = USE THICKNESS STATISTICS               **  C18  150
C*                       .NE. 0 = USER DEFINES THICKNESS            **  C18  160
C*                                                                  **  C18  170
C*           CALT     -  CIRRUS BASE ALTITUDE (KM)                  **  C18  180
C*                       0 = USE CALCULATED VALUE                   **  C18  190
C*                       .NE. 0 = USER DEFINES BASE ALTITUDE        **  C18  200
C*                                                                  **  C18  210
C*           ICLD     -  CIRRUS PRESENCE FLAG                       **  C18  220
C*                       0 = NO CIRRUS                              **  C18  230
C*                       18  19 = USE CIRRUS PROFILE                **  C18  240
C*                                                                  **  C18  250
C*           MODEL    -  ATMOSPHERIC MODEL                          **  C18  260
C*                       1-5  AS IN MAIN PROGRAM                    **  C18  270
C*                       MODEL = 0,6,7 NOT USED SET TO 2            **  C18  280
C*                                                                  **  C18  290
C*  OUTPUTS]                                                        **  C18  300
C*         CTHIK        -  CIRRUS THICKNESS (KM)                    **  C18  310
C*         CALT         -  CIRRUS BASE ALTITUDE (KM)                **  C18  320
C          CEXT IS THE EXTINCTION COEFFIENT(KM-1) AT 0.55               C18  330
C               DEFAULT VALUE 0.14*CTHIK                                C18  340
C*                                                                  **  C18  350
